# Server Setup Patterns

Comprehensive guide to server configuration and middleware patterns in the @web service.

## Server Architecture

### React Router v7 (Remix) Server

The application runs on React Router v7 with server-side rendering and API routes:

```tsx
// Entry point configuration
import { createRequestHandler } from "@react-router/express";
import express from "express";

const app = express();

// Middleware setup
app.use(express.json({ limit: "50mb" }));
app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: true }));

// Request handler
app.all(
  "*",
  createRequestHandler({
    build: await import("./build/server/index.js"),
  })
);
```

